edu.ucla.sspace.graph.isomorphism
Class TypedVF2State

java.lang.Object
  edu.ucla.sspace.graph.isomorphism.TypedVF2State
All Implemented Interfaces:
State
public class TypedVF2State
extends Object
implements State

A State implementation for testing isomorphism using the VF2 algorithm's logic with type constraints on the edges. Note that this implementation requires that the graphs have contiguous vertex indices (beginning at 0 to g.order()-1.

This implementation is an extension of the vf2_state implemenation in VFLib.
